        "column_PkLqfV": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "post_author": "Jason Park",
            "post_author_avatar": "shopify://shop_images/5a4ad2a8-9e68-4394-910b-e2f10850e1d9_-_Copy.png",
            "post_author_verified": false,
            "post_time": "1 Day ago",
            "post_text": "<p>This electric brush makes shower cleaning so much easier and saves a lot of time. The grout and corners came out spotless with far less manual effort. It is comfortable to hold but can be awkward at some angles. The battery lasts a long time, and it’s powerful enough with a couple of speed settings to handle tough spots. USB rechargeable. The extendable handle is also a huge help for reaching high or tight areas. I’ve only used it once so far, but I’m already very impressed!<br/><br/></p>",
            "post_image": "shopify://shop_images/81eFGFDufvL.jpg",
            "post_reactions": "like, love, care",
            "post_reactions_text": "2.1k",
            "post_comments_text": "236 Comments",
            "comment_1_author": "Comment author",
