        "column_BgX46J": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "post_author": "Emily ChenEmily Chen",
            "post_author_avatar": "shopify://shop_images/lady_1_prod.webp",
            "post_author_verified": false,
            "post_time": "5h ago",
            "post_text": "<p>By golly it helped a lot!!! A few more tries and maybe it’ll all be gone. With bad knees I would sit on edge of tub to try to clean it, but as you can see, didn’t work. The non-slip spots would never get clean. This tool did a pretty good job. Took a few rounds and cleaners, but sure is a lot better than before. I’m sure I can use this in other places in my home. </p><p>100% recommend it.<br/><br/></p>",
            "post_image": "shopify://shop_images/619X--i18WL.jpg",
            "post_reactions": "like, love, care",
